"{\"uid\": \"independent.ie-irish-news-taoiseach-tells-mary-lou-mcdonald-she-would-win-an-olympic-gold-medal-in-fluency-and-verbosity-in-dail-housing-row-a20526085.html\", \"text\": \"Taoiseach tells Mary Lou McDonald that if verbosity was an Olympic sport she would win gold  The Taoiseach has told Mary Lou McDonald that if \\\"fluency and verbosity\\\" were an Olympic sport she would win a gold medal.  The pair engaged in a row after the Sinn F\\u00e9in leader argued the report of the Housing Commission revealed the Government had paid out \\u20ac10 billion in accommodation supports since 2011 - with nothing to show for it.\"}"